ramadan abdallah shallah , the damascus-based leader of islamic holy war , said martyrs from his movement had carried out the jerusalem attack in response to israel 's settlement policy and judaization of the west bank. at the market , some 200 observant jews gathered saturday night near the site of the bombing to offer prayers of thanks that no lives other than those of the assailants were lost. that evening , when concerned members of the sughayer family gathered to await news of their missing relative , a man arrived and told them that he had sold his car